data.description: *Professional Photos Coming* Welcome home to this charming ranch style home located in the desirable Grenloch Terrace section of Washington Township.  This 3 bedroom, 1 full bathroom home has been freshly painted and is ready to move in!  Plenty of storage available in the floored attic with pull down stair access, there is a Bilco door style basement, partially built-in pool with attached deck (sold as-is), and large, fully fenced yard perfect for outdoor entertaining.  Conveniently located near popular shopping and dining attraction with easy access to major roadways!  2019 HVAC and Tankless Water Heater.
